A system for grouping together values into non-overlapping groups. This is used to figure out which values can be stored together based on how they are created

Types

Group[T] = ref object
  values: seq[T]
  indexes: Table[T, int]
A group of values that can be stored together 
Grouper[T] = object
  groups: HashSet[HashSet[T]]
Tracks state while calculating groups 
GroupTable[T] = object
  groups: HashSet[Group[T]]
  lookup: Table[T, Group[T]]
Maps values to the group they belong to
